%html
  %head
    %link{ href:'http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lobster', rel:'stylesheet', type:'text/css'}
    %link{ href:'http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Arvo:400,700', rel:'stylesheet', type:'text/css' }
    :css
      h1 {
        font-family: 'Lobster', cursive;
        font-size: 52px;
      }
      h3, p {
        font-family: 'Arvo', serif;
      }
  %body
    %h1 Exposition

    %h2 Write more with our daily inspiration.

    %p Write a short story based on the character and setting below. Come back tomorrow for a new challenge.

    %p A character:

    %h3
      = @exposition.person.capitalize

    %p A setting:

    %h3
      = @exposition.place.capitalize

    %p Sign in with Twitter or Facebook to post your story here.
